Thank you for all the birthday wishes and for everyone that came out last night. Thank you to my lovely friends for making my night special. My heart is full ❤️🥰🌞⭐️

Wow full circle moment this past weekend! I starred in my first acting project. Watched myself on the big screen and performed for the  audience a song so dear to my heart that I wrote/produced  last year ( which was also in the film✨). Thank you so much Julian for giving me the platform to express myself and really push myself emotionally  in a way that I never have before. This was such an experience and I’m grateful to all of the cast and crew for their incredible work that created “Leopards”  @leopardsfilm
